ngs abide by Your Will, not Your Words, and abstain from Your Prohibitions by Your Will. You are Him whom the people call in the event of urgent matters; and You are the refuge unto whom to run for help when misfortune strikes! Nothing would be fended off from them unless You fend it off! And nothing would be removed from them unless You remove it.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَجَرٰى بِطَاعَتِكَ الْقَضَاۗءُ وَمَضَتْ عَلٰى اِرَادَتِكَ الْاَشْيَاۗءُ فَهِيَ بِمَشِيَّتِكَ دُوْنَ قَوْلِكَ مُؤْتَمِرَةٌ وَبِاِرَادَتِكَ دُوْنَ نَهْيِكَ مُنْزَجِرَةٌ اَنْتَ الْمَدْعُوُّ لِلْمُهِمَّاتِ وَاَنْتَ الْمَفْزَعُ لِلْمُلِمَّاتِ (فِي الْمُلِمَّاتِ) لَا يَنْدَفِعُ مِنْهَا اِلَّا مَا دَفَعْتَ وَلَا يَنْكَشِفُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015342, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Lord! Now a calamity has descended upon me whose seriousness overburdens me and it is difficult for me to bear. You have sent it to me by Your Power and have directed it to me by Your Authority. Thus no one can push away what You have Willed and no one can impose what You Fend Off. No one can open what You close, and no one can close what You open. No one can ease what You make difficult and no one can make difficult what You ease. No one can help one You debase and no one can debase one You help. Please bestow Your Blessings on Muhammad and his Progeny.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "يَا رَبِّ مَا قَدْ تَكَاَّدَنِيْ ثِقْلُهٗ وَاَلَمَّ بِيْ مَا قَدْ بَهَظَنِيْ حَمْلُهٗ وَبِقُدْرَتِكَ اَوْرَدْتَهٗ عَلَيَّ وَبِسُلْطَانِكَ وَجَّهْتَهٗ اِلَيَّ وَلَا (فَلَا) مُصْدِرَ لِمَا اَوْرَدْتَ وَلَا مُوْرِدَ لِمَا اَصْدَرْتَ وَلَا 