r to alleviate what has happened to me and fend off what I am stuck in. And please bestow Your Blessings on Muhammad and his Progeny and do so for me even if I do not deserve it. O Benevolent Lord of the Throne! The Great King! O the best to talk to privately and the best to point to with our hands!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "(يَا رَبِ) لِمَا نَزَلَ بِيْ ذَرْعًا وَامْتَلَاْتُ بِمَا (بِحَمْلِ مَا) حَدَثَ عَلَيَّ هَمًّا وَاَنْتَ الْقَادِرُ عَلٰى كَشْفِ مَا مُنِيْتُ بِهٖ وَدَفْعِ مَا وَقَعْتُ فِيْهِ فَصَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَافْعَلْ بِيْ ذٰلِكَ وَاِنْ لَمْ اَسْتَوْجِبْهُ مِنْكَ يَا رَبِّ يَا ذَا الْعَرْشِ الْكَرِيْمِ (الْعَظِيْمِ) وَالسُّلْطَانِ الْعَظِيْمِ (الْقَدِيْمِ) يَا خَيْرَ مَنْ خَلَوْنَا بِهٖ وَحْدَنَا وَيَا خَيْرَ مَنْ اَشَرْنَا اِلَيْهِ بِكَفِّنَا نَسْئَلُكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueS